PSD-LA-800 & 3136-V1 (issued 12/14/2015; application for permit modification submitted 6/8/2020; additional information submitted 5/10/2021) -- This permit renewal/modification application does not involve any construction, modification, or reconstruction activities, or any other physical changes or changes in the method of operation at the Ethylene Plant (LACC, LLC US).

public comments:
